column2: select sl.stable_id as case_list_id, max (sl.name) as case_list_name , max (sl.description) as case_list_description , sl.cancer_study_id , STRING_AGG (s.stable_id , #) as case_ids from cancer_study cs , sample_list sl , sample_list_list sll , sample s where cs.cancer_study_identifier = # and sl.CANCER_STUDY_ID = cs.CANCER_STUDY_ID and sl.list_id = sll.list_id and s.internal_id = sll.sample_id group by sl.stable_id, sl.cancer_study_id order by #, # select top # * from sys.dm_exec_external_work order by end_time DESC
